ITV.La.Course.by.Le.Tour.2014.PDTV.x264-NX

Sunday 27th July 2014 ITV4
1pm to 2pm Live

The inaugural edition of La Course by Le Tour takes place on the Champs Elysees today coinciding with the final stage of the Tour de France. A few hours before the men arrive, the elite of women's cycling will race twelve laps of a 7km circuit past the Arc de Triomphe, the quays of the Seine, and the Rue de Rivoli before hitting the finishing straight on the Champ-Elysees itself. The winner of this race will go down in the history books. Presented by Gary Imlach. Commentary by Anthony McCrossan and Rochelle Gilmore.
